&=s_1(\alpha(\delta))\bullet\underline{\alpha(\delta)^*r_1'(\delta)^{-1}}\bullet  \underline{\alpha(\delta)^*g'(\delta,\underline{p})}  \bullet \underline{\alpha(\delta)^*r_2'(\delta)}\bullet s_2(\alpha(\delta))^{-1}\\
